Are you team Handheld or team Laptop? 

@Acer  just released the new Aspire X Gaming Laptop with up to Intel Core Ultra X9 Series 3 Processors. I’m able to play smoothly completely unplugged with Intel Arc B390 Integrated graphics (even snuck in gameplay at a Taiwan Temple) on the 3K OLED display. 

If you are team Handheld, they just dropped the new Acer Predator Atlas 8 with the new Intel Arc G3 and G3 Extreme processors. It’s also the first handheld to feature a metal fan for 10% increased ai
